title: The Brick Lady & The Gender Wars | OLAY & FRIENDS
description:
A story went viral after Rho, a woman now referred to as the brick lady, claimed she was assaulted by a man with a brick and other men saw and didn’t intervene. The internet’s gender wars made it go viral. Now, Houston PD is claiming she lied about being hit with the brick and that they have video footage showing her get into a man’s car and hit him before the man hits her with a bottle. Now they’re charging her with fraud for gofundme proceeds she never received. We unpack everything here on OLAY & FRIENDS
